==Almanac==
Elections are held the first Tuesday after November 1st. Members of the [[Delaware General Assembly]] take office the second Tuesday of January. [[Delaware Senate |State Senators]] have a four year term. The [[Governor of Delaware |Governor]] takes office the third Tuesday of January and has a four year term. 

